title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum Stadium on 1991-02-21
lineage: Dat Master > Dat 1 > 16 bit 48kHz DAT Clone > TASCAM DA-20 (SPDIF out) ->  LynxTWO-B Audio Reference Interface (SPDIF in) ->  Wavelab 6.0 > Weiss Saracon for 16 BIT 44.1kHz SRC and POWR-3 Dither  Tracked in CDwave, FLACd Flac Frontend level 8 Tag & Rename for FLAC Meta-Tagging
description:
Set 1

Help On The Way ->
Slipknot! ->
Franklin's Tower 
Little Red Rooster 
Loser 
Stuck Inside Of Mobile With The Memphis Blues Again 
Tennessee Jed 
The Promised Land 

Set 2

Playing In The Band   ->
Uncle John's Band   
Terrapin Station  ->
Jam  ->
Drums* ->
Space ->
Eyes Of The World**  
Throwing Stones ->
Not Fade Away** 

Encore
Knockin' On Heaven's Door 

* with Airto Moreira on percussion
** with Dragon Parade (for Chinese New Year)

reviews.review_text: Show smokes, AUD smokes Damn - right off the bat! By 4 min in you already know it's gonna be a silky silky crazy crazy night

crowd noise killer audio
Crowd noise cardioids :-(
Oh what a night.. the parade was a mind blower.... this show was some kind of magic, i miss those days..
Uncle Jack I was present, this one of the best shows! The Dragon Parade was spectacular. I can close my eyes and still see it all!
